sources.title: The Sphinx (restored, colorized) (1933, crime, imdb score: 5.6)
sources.description: The Sphinx is a 1933 American Pre-Code mystery drama film directed by Phil Rosen . The film was remade by William Beaudine as Phantom Killer in 1942.
